# 🔐 service_account.json (REQUIRED FOR LOCAL COMPILER)

The file 'service_account.json' is missing from this repository for security reasons. 
This file is required to allow the GooTeX local compiler to download text from Google Docs.

### 👥 For Co-Authors/Team Members:
If you are working on a shared project, DO NOT generate your own key. 
Please contact the Project Lead (Host) to receive the official 'service_account.json' file.
Once received, place it in the root directory of this project on your local machine.

### 🚀 For Project Leads (New Setup):
If you are setting up a brand new GooTeX environment:
1. Go to the Google Cloud Console.
2. Create a Service Account and download the JSON Key.
3. Name it 'service_account.json'.
4. Ensure the email address of this Service Account is shared with 'Editor' 
   permissions on your Google Doc.

---
⚠️ WARNING: NEVER commit the actual .json file to GitHub. 
It is already included in .gitignore to prevent accidental leaks.